summary: This is a witness list filed by the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York in the criminal case against Ghislaine Maxwell (20 Cr. 330). The document is designated as confidential under a protective order dated July 31, 2020.

keyFacts: The document is a confidential witness list for the criminal case against Ghislaine Maxwell (20 Cr. 330).
It is governed by a protective order dated July 31, 2020, restricting its disclosure.
The list was filed by the U.S. Attorney's Office, led by Damian Williams, on October 11, 2021.
The witness list itself is not included in this excerpt, only the cover page and filing information.
